screen_name: So I tested negative for the COVID-19 but my symptoms remain.  Still have breathing issues, tightness in the chest,  chills,  fatigue.  Tuta says that's your body still healing from the effects of the virus.  So good to go!
I recieved a positive COVID-19 test today.   Dr. Huan....will Ohitashi really help??  I have shortness of breath, tight feeling in my chest, dry warm scratchy throat, slight body aches right now.
